<lb n="0580a16"/><head type="no">No. 1137 [Nos. 1138-1140]</head>
<lb n="0580a17"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0580001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，〔佛說〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0580001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">【原】麗本，〔佛說〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0580001"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0580001" place="foot" type="rest">【原】麗本</note>善法方便陀羅<note n="0580002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼＋（&CB00057;）【三】＊</note><note n="0580002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼＋（&CB00057;）【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0580002"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">尼&CB00057;</rdg></app>經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0580a18"/>
<lb n="0580a19"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0580003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名〕－【宋】</note><app n="0580003"><lem>人名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0580004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔今〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0580004"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>附東晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0580a20"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時佛住摩竭提界寂滅道場菩
<lb n="0580a21"/>提樹下。與比丘僧大眾俱集。其名曰大智舍
<lb n="0580a22"/>利弗。長老目揵連。長老阿難。大聲聞等。及諸
<lb n="0580a23"/>菩薩摩訶薩眾。金剛幢菩薩。金剛藏菩薩。彌
<lb n="0580a24"/>勒菩薩。如是賢劫諸大菩薩摩訶薩眾。時執
<lb n="0580a25"/>金剛神白佛言。世尊如來應供正遍知者。如
<lb n="0580a26"/>實知見是善方便陀羅尼&CB00057;光明威力。勢能
<lb n="0580a27"/>摧滅一切諸惡。無覆護者能作覆護。若遇一
<lb n="0580a28"/>切惡緣知識。毒龍諸鬼夜叉羅剎。及多那若
<lb n="0580a29"/>鳩槃<note n="0580005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【宋】【元】</note><app n="0580005"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app>人非人等。怖畏刀<note n="0580006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">杖＝仗【三】</note><note n="0580006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">杖＝仗【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580006"><lem>杖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">仗</rdg></app>怨家橫害。邪
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1137.0580b" n="0580b"/>
<lb n="0580b01"/>魅<note n="0580007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01679;＝厭【三】</note><note n="0580007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01679;＝厭【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580007"><lem>&CB01679;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">厭</rdg></app>禱不能嬈亂。至四威儀行住坐臥不捨
<lb n="0580b02"/>眾生。如我今者侍衛如來未曾暫離。是陀羅
<lb n="0580b03"/>尼於一切時。覆護眾生利益眾生。初不放捨
<lb n="0580b04"/>亦復如是。是故我今勸請如來說此陀羅尼。
<lb n="0580b05"/>此陀羅尼即是菩薩即是大乘。何以故若善
<lb n="0580b06"/>男子善女人。無覆護者能為覆護。悉滅一切
<lb n="0580b07"/>&CB00508;訟繫縛諸&CB00240;橫故</p>
<lb n="0580b08"/><p>是時佛告執金剛神。善哉善哉執金剛神如
<lb n="0580b09"/>汝所說。乃能如是為眾生故勸請如來。汝今
<lb n="0580b10"/>諦聽當為汝說善法方便陀羅尼&CB00057;。爾時世
<lb n="0580b11"/>尊即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0580b12"/><p type="dharani">優鳩<note place="inline">一</note>茂鳩<note place="inline">二</note>摩毘<note n="0580008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼＝呢【三】＊</note><note n="0580008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼＝呢【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0580008"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">呢</rdg></app><note place="inline">奴利<note n="0580009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】</note><app n="0580009"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app>三</note>摩陀尼<note place="inline">四</note>婆羅
<lb n="0580b13"/>遮&CB00619;<note place="inline">五</note>那休休梨越多莎呵<note place="inline">六</note></p>
<lb n="0580b14"/><p>是時如來應正遍知。說是莊嚴大頂勝王陀
<lb n="0580b15"/>羅尼已。告執金剛。汝當如是憶念受持。如來
<lb n="0580b16"/>今當更為汝說。即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0580b17"/><p type="dharani">跋逝唻<note place="inline">一</note>跋逝<note n="0580010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唻＝來【明】</note><app n="0580010"><lem>唻</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">來</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note>跋逝唻陀利<note place="inline">三</note>跋逝唻婆
<lb n="0580b18"/>帝<note place="inline">四</note>跋逝唻陛帝<note place="inline">五</note>跋逝唻達提<note place="inline">六</note>灼迦囉跋
<lb n="0580b19"/>逝唻<note place="inline">七</note>灼迦囉陀唎<note place="inline">八</note>陀唎<note place="inline">九</note>陀唎<note place="inline">十</note>婆<note n="0580011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00074;＝唎【三】</note><note n="0580011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00074;＝唎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580011"><lem>&CB00074;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">唎</rdg></app><note place="inline">十一</note>
<lb n="0580b20"/>茂唎<note place="inline">十二</note>遮唎<note place="inline">十三</note>休休唎<note place="inline">十四</note>朋伽<note place="inline">十五</note>毘毘
<lb n="0580b21"/>利<note place="inline">十六</note>唎唎尸<note place="inline">十七</note>唎尸<note n="0580012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唎＝利【三】＊</note><note n="0580012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唎＝利【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0580012"><lem>唎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app><note place="inline">十八</note>嘍嘍旨<note place="inline">十九</note>遮
<lb n="0580b22"/>&CB00619;<note place="inline">二十</note>周唎<note place="inline">二十一</note>茂<anchor id="fxT20p0580b01"/>唎<note place="inline">二十二</note>曼<note n="0580013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【三】</note><note n="0580013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝荼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580013"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app>唎<note place="inline">二十三</note>薩波
<lb n="0580b23"/>波<note n="0580014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毘＋（那）【三】</note><note n="0580014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毘＋（那）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580014"><lem>毘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">毘那</rdg></app>賒兜<note place="inline">二十四</note>&CB00306;&CB00306;兜比唎<note place="inline">二十五</note>摩唻<note place="inline">二十六</note>呵多
<lb n="0580b24"/>尼<note place="inline">二十七</note>婆唻<note place="inline">二十八</note>婆唻<note place="inline">二十九</note>婆地<note place="inline">三十</note>跋提<note place="inline">三十一</note>毘題
<lb n="0580b25"/><note place="inline">三十二</note>毘唻<note place="inline">三十三</note>嘍娑唻<note place="inline">三十四</note>舍囉鞞<note place="inline">三十五</note>囉<note n="0580015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝婆【三】</note><note n="0580015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑＝婆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580015"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>
<lb n="0580b26"/>泥<note place="inline">三十六</note>囉婆那唻曳<note place="inline">三十七</note>&CB01227;<note place="inline">父藍反</note>摩遮唎那<note place="inline">三十八</note>因
<lb n="0580b27"/>陀跋帝<note place="inline">三十九</note>提提<note n="0580016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【三】＊</note><note n="0580016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅＝囉【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0580016"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>耶<note place="inline">四十</note>那謨摩醯首<anchor id="fxT20p0580b02"/>羅耶
<lb n="0580b28"/>尼<note place="inline">四十一</note>利師&CB01227;<note place="inline">父藍反</note>跋尼<note place="inline">四十二</note>波波瞻婆尼<note place="inline">四十三</note>柯
<lb n="0580b29"/>羅婆提<note place="inline">四十四</note>浮多婆提<note place="inline">四十五</note>薩誃<note place="inline">&CB00337;邪反</note>柯梯<note place="inline">四十六</note>蘇
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1137.0580c" n="0580c"/>
<lb n="0580c01"/>摩婆提<note place="inline">四十七</note>蘇摩&CB03875;<note n="0580017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02978;＋（&CB03778;）【三】</note><note n="0580017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02978;＋（&CB03778;）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580017"><lem>&CB02978;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB02978;&CB03778;</rdg></app>莎呵<note place="inline">四十八</note></p>
<lb n="0580c02"/><p>佛告執金剛。復當為汝更說神&CB00057;。能令行者
<lb n="0580c03"/>現得長壽。即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0580c04"/><p type="dharani">呵囉<note place="inline">一</note>呵囉<note place="inline">二</note>嘻囉<note place="inline">三</note></p>
<lb n="0580c05"/><p>時執金剛即白佛言。唯然世尊我當受持</p>
<lb n="0580c06"/><p type="dharani">迦致多<note place="inline">一</note>波致多<note place="inline">二</note>阿夷那<note place="inline">三</note>呵唎瞻婆尼<note place="inline">四</note>柯
<lb n="0580c07"/>葛旦尼<note place="inline">五</note>頞哆<note place="inline">轉舌音</note><note n="0580018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿＝陀【三】</note><note n="0580018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿＝陀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0580018"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">陀</rdg></app>呵尼<note place="inline">六</note>末伽毘嚧呵尼
<lb n="0580c08"/><note place="inline">七</note>休娑婆帝<note place="inline">八</note>復娑婆帝<note place="inline">九</note>嘻<note place="inline">喜梨反</note>利<note place="inline">十</note>嘻利<note place="inline">十一</note>
<lb n="0580c09"/>耶他嗜<note place="inline">十二</note>耶他忌尼<note place="inline">十三</note>耶他波爛遮<note place="inline">十四</note>耶
<lb n="0580c10"/>他婆<note n="0580019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">檐＝擔【三】＊</note><note n="0580019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">檐＝擔【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0580019"><lem>檐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">擔</rdg></app><note place="inline">十五</note>耶他&CB00393;陀<anchor id="fxT20p0580c01"/>檐<note place="inline">十六</note></p>
<lb n="0580c11"/><p>說是&CB00057;已告執金剛。如是善法陀羅尼&CB00057;如
<lb n="0580c12"/>來所說。為利一切諸眾生故。大慈悲故。我今
<lb n="0580c13"/>當更為汝說之。如昔如來應正遍知如是妙
<lb n="0580c14"/>說。去來今佛之所印可誠實不虛。爾時世尊
<lb n="0580c15"/>即放大人眉間相光。遍照一切諸佛剎土。是
<lb n="0580c16"/>光所照普能利益無量眾生。彼方諸佛見是
<lb n="0580c17"/>光已。各從坐起咸共尋光來至忍土。至此土
<lb n="0580c18"/>已同聲讚言。善哉釋迦牟尼世尊善能付囑。
<lb n="0580c19"/>利益安樂一切眾生。善哉善哉釋迦如來應
<lb n="0580c20"/>正遍知。為利一切諸眾生故。為覆護故為照
<lb n="0580c21"/>明故。為令眾生得歡喜故。說是善法陀羅尼
<lb n="0580c22"/>&CB00057;。我等諸佛所說章句亦皆如是。善哉釋迦
<lb n="0580c23"/>能廣施者。若善男子及善女人。聞是善法陀
<lb n="0580c24"/>羅尼&CB00057;欲得利益。應於晨朝受持讀誦。即為
<lb n="0580c25"/>我等諸佛所護。若有誦持此&CB00057;之處則為吉
<lb n="0580c26"/>祥。我等諸佛皆在中故。若諸眾生先來所造。
<lb n="0580c27"/>極重惡業皆滅無餘。能令此諸善男子等。具
<lb n="0580c28"/>足獲得二十善利。一者現得長壽。二者舍宅
<lb n="0580c29"/>安隱。三者名譽遠聞。四者現得尊貴。五者多
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1137.0581a" n="0581a"/>
<lb n="0581a01"/>宜財寶。六者威貌殊勝。七者勇<note n="0581001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捍＝悍【元】【明】</note><app n="0581001"><lem>捍</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">悍</rdg></app>無畏。八
<lb n="0581a02"/>者無諸疾病。九者安隱快樂。十者進行無倦。
<lb n="0581a03"/>十一<note n="0581002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0581002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0581002"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>諸佛護念。十二<anchor id="fxT20p0581a01"/>者諸天守護。十三
<lb n="0581a04"/>人所愛敬。十四現見諸佛。十五善友所護。十
<lb n="0581a05"/>六毒害不加。十七惡鬼降伏。十八怨敵自消。
<lb n="0581a06"/>十九眷屬成就。二十善願從心。如是執金剛。
<lb n="0581a07"/>是陀羅尼<note n="0581003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00057;〕－【三】</note><note n="0581003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔&CB00057;〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0581003"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>即是諸佛微密藏處。一切諸佛
<lb n="0581a08"/>之所護念。真實不虛微妙善說</p>
<lb n="0581a09"/><p>時執金剛神白佛言。世尊我於如來所說神
<lb n="0581a10"/>&CB00057;。亦當隨喜信樂演說。所以者何是陀羅尼
<lb n="0581a11"/>神&CB00057;勢力。無覆護者能為覆護。多利益故。為
<lb n="0581a12"/>如是等諸善男子善女人故。我今當更演說
<lb n="0581a13"/>善法陀羅尼&CB00057;。欲得安樂及求度者。是諸行
<lb n="0581a14"/>人應於晨朝受持讀誦。則得神&CB00057;擁護之力。
<lb n="0581a15"/>必當永離一切苦惱。即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0581a16"/><p type="dharani">尸棄<note place="inline">一</note>尸棄<note place="inline">二</note>支至<note place="inline">三</note>支至<note place="inline">四</note>婆&CB01226;<note place="inline">五</note>婆&CB01226;<note place="inline">六</note>嚧
<lb n="0581a17"/>嘍<note place="inline">七</note>嚧嘍<note place="inline">八</note>時嗜<note place="inline">九</note>時嗜<note place="inline">十</note>咖囉<note place="inline">十一</note>咖囉<note place="inline">十二</note>
<lb n="0581a18"/><note n="0581004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03873;＝&CB14336;【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0581004"><lem>&CB03873;</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB14336;</rdg></app>嘻<note place="inline">十三</note><anchor id="fxT20p0581a02"/>&CB03873;嘻<note place="inline">十四</note>頗破<note place="inline">十五</note>頗破<note place="inline">十六</note>磨系<note place="inline">十
<lb n="0581a19"/>七</note>磨系<note place="inline">十八</note>呵那<note place="inline">十九</note>呵那<note place="inline">二十</note>呵那<note place="inline">二十一</note>馱呵<note place="inline">二十二</note>
<lb n="0581a20"/>馱呵<note place="inline">二十三</note>馱呵<note place="inline">二十四</note>波遮<note place="inline">二十五</note>波遮<note place="inline">二十六</note>莎呵<note n="0581005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二十七〕－【宋】</note><app n="0581005"><lem><note place="inline">二十七</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0581a21"/><p>是時世尊告執金剛。善哉善哉執金剛神。是
<lb n="0581a22"/>陀羅尼最神最驗。為諸眾生是故說之。此陀
<lb n="0581a23"/>羅尼神&CB00057;威力。悉能障蔽一一毛孔。令諸龍
<lb n="0581a24"/>鬼一切疾疫。眾邪毒氣不能得入。亦能為作
<lb n="0581a25"/>解脫因緣</p>
<lb n="0581a26"/><p>爾時三千大千界主大梵天王。即從座起為佛
<lb n="0581a27"/>作禮。合掌向佛而白佛言。善哉世尊我今亦
<lb n="0581a28"/>樂讚揚隨喜利益成就。諸善男子行此&CB00057;者。
<lb n="0581a29"/>應於晨朝受持讀誦是陀羅尼。如今世尊為
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1137.0581b" n="0581b"/>
<lb n="0581b01"/>欲利安擁護如是諸眾生故。說此善法陀羅
<lb n="0581b02"/>尼&CB00057;時。大梵王即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0581b03"/><p type="dharani"><anchor id="fxT20p0581b01"/>&CB03873;利<note place="inline">一</note>彌利<note place="inline">二</note>旨利莎呵<note place="inline">三</note>&CB01227;摩富唎莎呵<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0581b04"/>&CB01227;摩&CB03778;莎呵<note place="inline">五</note>波劫&CB03778;<note place="inline">六</note>弗巴僧怛唎莎呵<note place="inline">七</note></p>
<lb n="0581b05"/><p>說是&CB00057;已即白佛言。大德勝尊如是所說陀
<lb n="0581b06"/>羅尼&CB00057;能悉擁護。是善男子及善女人。亦能
<lb n="0581b07"/>令得增益壽命。是故行者應當晨朝。如法讀
<lb n="0581b08"/>誦修行受持。爾時釋提桓因復白佛言。世尊
<lb n="0581b09"/>我今亦欲利益擁護如是善男子故。說是陀
<lb n="0581b10"/>羅尼者諸佛世尊之所護念。是故行者若欲
<lb n="0581b11"/>得是陀羅尼&CB00057;功德利者。應於晨朝讀誦受
<lb n="0581b12"/>持。是時帝釋即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0581b13"/><p type="dharani">毘尼婆<note n="0581006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【三】</note><note n="0581006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0581006"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>泥<note place="inline">一</note>婆陀磨&CB02258;帝<note place="inline">二</note>致致致<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0581007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懼＋（陀）【三】</note><note n="0581007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懼＋（陀）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0581007"><lem>懼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">懼陀</rdg></app>
<lb n="0581b14"/>利乾陀唎<note place="inline">四</note>摩<note n="0581008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【明】</note><app n="0581008"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>摩羅婆<note place="inline">五</note>呵那末彈陀羅尼
<lb n="0581b15"/><note place="inline">六</note>陀羅摩利尼<note place="inline">七</note>斫迦婆&CB03757;<note place="inline">八</note>扇跋<anchor id="fxT20p0581b02"/>唎<note place="inline">九</note>扇婆
<lb n="0581b16"/>唎莎呵<note place="inline">十</note></p>
<lb n="0581b17"/><p>爾時復有四大天王毘沙門天王提頭賴吒天
<lb n="0581b18"/>王毘樓勒叉天王毘樓博叉天王。合掌恭敬
<lb n="0581b19"/>而白佛言。我等四王亦當為護是善男子善女
<lb n="0581b20"/>人等。樂欲修行是善方便陀羅尼者。彼諸眾
<lb n="0581b21"/>生亦應晨朝受持讀誦。爾時四王即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0581b22"/><p type="dharani">弗巴<note place="inline">一</note>修<note n="0581009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弗＝佛【宋】</note><app n="0581009"><lem>弗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">佛</rdg></app>巴<note place="inline">二</note>頭摩波<note n="0581010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝唎【三】</note><note n="0581010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＝唎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0581010"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">唎</rdg></app>呵唻<note place="inline">三</note>阿唎波
<lb n="0581b23"/>羅世帝<note place="inline">四</note>扇帝<note place="inline">五</note>涅目帝<note place="inline">六</note>&CB04249;伽&CB00619;<note place="inline">七</note>兜帝<note place="inline">八</note>兜
<lb n="0581b24"/>帝莎呵<note place="inline">九</note></p>
<lb n="0581b25"/><p>爾時釋迦牟尼如來。即舉右手告天帝釋大
<lb n="0581b26"/>梵天王及四護世。善哉善哉大德諸天乃能
<lb n="0581b27"/>於是善法方便陀羅尼王隨喜演說。如此善
<lb n="0581b28"/>法陀羅尼者。皆是諸佛之所護念。汝等應當
<lb n="0581b29"/>常善受持</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1137.0581c" n="0581c"/>
<lb n="0581c01"/><p>爾時世尊又復重告執金剛神。善哉善哉執
<lb n="0581c02"/>金剛神。是善方便及得長壽陀羅尼&CB00057;。此<note n="0581011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【三】</note><note n="0581011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝二【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0581011"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>
<lb n="0581c03"/>&CB00057;者。皆是十方諸佛如來之所護念稱讚印
<lb n="0581c04"/>可。諸天天王大力鬼神之所守護。若善男子
<lb n="0581c05"/>善女人等。欲修行者。應當自淨身口意已。於
<lb n="0581c06"/>晨朝時以殷重心。如法受持淨心讀誦。能如
<lb n="0581c07"/>是者不見天龍諸惡人鬼。有能加害得其便
<lb n="0581c08"/>者。爾時菩薩聲聞大眾執金剛神。及諸天王
<lb n="0581c09"/>一切鬼神龍王夜叉人非人等。咸共恭敬皆
<lb n="0581c10"/>大歡喜受持奉行</p>
<lb n="0581c11"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><anchor id="fxT20p0581c01"/>佛說善法方便陀羅<anchor id="fxT20p0581c02"/>尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
